true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "72e7057", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"hero\">\n<div class=\"container hero-grid\">\n<div class=\"hero-text\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Bespoke Booking Systems</span>\n<h1>Beautiful booking software, built just for your bridal boutique.</h1>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p class=\"lead\">Ivory Digital gives your boutique its own elegant booking website <em>and</em> a powerful behind-the-scenes diary \u2014 fully branded to you. Brides book themselves online, your diary fills in automatically, and you never lose a fitting room to a double-booking again.</p>\n<div class=\"btn-row\">\n<a class=\"btn btn-gold\" href=\"/contact/\">Start Your Free 7-Day Trial</a>\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"/booking-system/\">See the System</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hero-visual\">\n<div class=\"frame\"><img alt=\"Ivory Digital booking system staff dashboard showing today's appointments\" height=\"888\" loading=\"eager\" src=\"__IVORY_BASE__/assets/img/screenshot-dashboard.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" width=\"1280\"/></div>\n<div class=\"hero-badge\"><strong>No platform fees</strong>Owned by you, hosted by us</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "8cc5bf3", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "80a6844", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Our Products</span>\n<h2>Three ways Ivory Digital helps your business grow.</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p class=\"lead\">From bridal boutiques to wedding photographers to small businesses of every kind \u2014 we build software and websites designed around exactly how you work.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container grid grid-3\">\n<div class=\"card\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">For Bridal Boutiques</span>\n<h3>Bridal Booking System</h3>\n<p>Your own branded booking website and staff diary in one. Brides book online, your diary fills automatically, and you never lose a fitting room to a double-booking again.</p>\n<div class=\"btn-row\"><a class=\"btn btn-gold\" href=\"/booking-system/\">Explore the Booking System</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">For Wedding Photographers</span>\n<h3>StudioApp Client Galleries</h3>\n<p>The complete client gallery &amp; delivery platform \u2014 branded galleries, video streaming, guest uploads, automated emails and print sales. From \u00a315/month.</p>\n<div class=\"btn-row\"><a class=\"btn btn-gold\" href=\"/studioapp/\">Explore StudioApp</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">For Small Businesses</span>\n<h3>Website Design &amp; SEO</h3>\n<p>Beautiful, fast, search-optimised websites \u2014 designed, built, hosted and ranked for you, at genuinely fair, low prices.</p>\n<div class=\"btn-row\"><a class=\"btn btn-gold\" href=\"/web-design-seo/\">Explore Web Design &amp; SEO</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "59735c5", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "1de3962", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"band-ivory2\">\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Your Brand, Not a Widget</span>\n<h2>Your own private booking website &amp; diary, in one.</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p class=\"lead\">There are no third-party booking-platform subscriptions and no per-booking fees. Your system is privately built, branded to your business, and supported with a simple hosting and maintenance package.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container grid grid-3\">\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"17\" rx=\"1\" width=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\"></rect><path d=\"M3 9h18M8 2v4M16 2v4\"></path></svg><h3>Smart booking engine</h3><p>Only genuinely free times are ever offered \u2014 respecting your hours, capacity and cleardown buffers. Two brides can never grab the same slot.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 3l9 9-9 9-9-9z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2.4\"></circle></svg><h3>Fully branded to you</h3><p>Your name, your colours, your photos \u2014 it looks like an extension of your boutique, not a generic third-party form.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M4 21V5a2 2 0 012-2h8l6 6v12z\"></path><path d=\"M14 3v6h6\"></path></svg><h3>One or many boutiques</h3><p>Run a single shop or several locations from one tidy control panel, each with its own hours, services and photos.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M18 8a6 6 0 10-12 0c0 7-3 8-3 8h18s-3-1-3-8\"></path><path d=\"M10.5 21a1.5 1.5 0 003 0\"></path></svg><h3>Fewer no-shows</h3><p>Automatic confirmation and reminder emails keep brides on track \u2014 all sent from your own address, and off until you switch them on.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M9 6h11M9 12h11M9 18h11M4 6h.01M4 12h.01M4 18h.01\"></path></svg><h3>Built-in waitlist</h3><p>When a day is full, brides join a waitlist instead of leaving \u2014 so you never lose a keen customer to a busy diary.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M3 3v18h18\"></path><path d=\"M7 14l3-3 3 3 5-6\"></path></svg><h3>Insightful analytics</h3><p>See your busiest days and times, no-show rates and exactly where your brides are coming from.</p></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "fc9a4b5", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "4abeb2e", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">How It Works</span>\n<h2>From first chat to fully live \u2014 handled for you.</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container steps\">\n<div class=\"step\"><h3>We build it</h3><p>We create your bespoke booking system and tailor the services, questions and opening hours to exactly how your boutique works.</p></div>\n<div class=\"step\"><h3>Branded to you</h3><p>We style it with your name, colours and photography so it feels seamless with your existing website and Instagram.</p></div>\n<div class=\"step\"><h3>Hosted &amp; supported</h3><p>We host it, keep it updated and back it up \u2014 all wrapped in a simple maintenance package. You just take the bookings.</p></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "8791052", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "9426718", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"band-ivory2\">\n<div class=\"container showcase\">\n<div class=\"showcase-text\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">The Bride's Experience</span>\n<h2>A calm, elegant booking journey.</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p>In a few gentle taps, a bride chooses your boutique, picks the appointment she wants, sees only the times you're truly free, and confirms \u2014 all on a page that looks and feels like <em>your</em> brand.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Works beautifully on phones, tablets and desktops.</li>\n<li>Instant confirmation with a reference and one-tap calendar add.</li>\n<li>She can reschedule or cancel herself \u2014 no phone tag.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"btn-row\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"/booking-system/\">Explore every feature</a></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"Bridal boutique online booking page \u2014 choose your boutique\" height=\"888\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__IVORY_BASE__/assets/img/screenshot-booking.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" width=\"1280\"/></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "3c31c66", "elType": "container", "settings": {"cont